## Adding New Features

1. Add business logic in `ProjectService.java`
2. Extend models if needed (`Task.java` or `Project.java`)
3. Update CLI in `TaskProjectManagerApp.java`
4. Write tests in appropriate test class

## Running Locally

Use IntelliJ IDEA or VS Code with Maven support.

## Code Style

- Follow standard Java naming conventions
- Use meaningful variable names
- Add Javadoc for public methods
